These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 9

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-1::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: march, january, july, october
There 4 different types of food: orange, peas, plum, watermelon
1. the person eating watermelon is not to the right of the person eating orange##8
2. the person eating watermelon is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
3. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in july##3
4. the person who's birthday is in october is somewhere to the right of the person eating peas##5
5. the person who's birthday is in october is not to the left of the person eating watermelon##8
6. the person eating plum is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in january##5
7. the person who's birthday is in january is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in march and the person eating peas##7
8. the person who's birthday is in january and the person eating watermelon have the same parity positions##9
9. the person who's birthday is in july and the person eating orange have different parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Nationality   | march | january | july     | october |
| Pet           | plum   | watermelon     | peas | orange  |

