.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-2::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  coachcher, doctor, mechanic, coach
The people use 4 different means of transport: skateboard, airplane, ship, bike
1. the person driving the skateboard is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person driving the bike and the doctor have the same parity positions##9
3. the person driving the airplane is not to the right of the person driving the ship##8
4. the person driving the skateboard is not to the right of the coach##8
5. the person driving the skateboard is somewhere to the left of the coachcher##5
6. the coachcher is somewhere to the right of the person driving the airplane##5
7. the doctor is somewhere to the right of the coachcher##5
8. the coach is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |      3      |     4     |
| Beverage   | coach     | mechanic    | coachcher | doctor    |
| Hobby      | skateboard | airplane | ship      | bike |

