.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-3::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, lacrosse, parkour, climbing
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: daisy, rose, tulip, orchid
1. the person who's sport is parkour is somewhere to the left of the person who growstulip##5
2. the person who growsdaisy is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is parkour##5
3. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1
4. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the far left##1
5. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1
6. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the person who growsdaisy##1
7. the person who growsdaisy is not to the left of the person who growsrose##8
8. the person who's sport is lacrosse and the person who growsrose have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |     3     |   4   |
| Beverage   | lacrosse    | parkour   | cricket    | climbing  |
| Food       | rose | orchid | daisy | tulip |

