.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-4::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: ritmeester, siglo, oliveros, bolivar
There are 4 different favourite colors: purple, aquamarine, yellow, amber
1. the person who likes purple is the siglo-smoker##1
2. the person who likes aquamarine is on the right of the person who likes yellow##1
3. the person who likes aquamarine is somewhere to the left of the siglo-smoker##5
4. the person who likes amber is on the left or right of the oliveros-smoker##3
5. the person who likes aquamarine is on the left of the ritmeester-smoker##1
6. the bolivar-smoker and the person who likes amber have the same parity positions##9
7. the oliveros-smoker is on the left or right of the ritmeester-smoker##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |       2        |   3    |     4      |
| Job           | bolivar | oliveros | ritmeester  | siglo |
| Music-Genre   | yellow             | aquamarine          | amber | purple    |

