.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-5::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: scientific, horror, sports, satire
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, lemonade, sprite, fanta
1. the person watching sports movies is not the person drinking sprite##6
2. the person drinking almond-milk and the person watching scientific movies have different parity positions##9
3. the person drinking lemonade and the person watching horror movies have different parity positions##9
4. the person drinking lemonade is somewhere to the left of the person watching sports movies##5
5. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1
6. the person watching horror movies is not the person drinking lemonade##6
7. the person watching satire movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching horror movies##5
8. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1
9. the person drinking fanta is not the person watching satire movies##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |    3     |     4     |
| Music-Genre   | scientific | sports | satire  | horror |
| Pet           | lemonade   | almond-milk     | sprite | fanta      |

