.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-6::.
4 different pets are kept: pony, ferret, turtle, bird
City: edinburgh, venice, marseilles, hannover
1. the owner of the ferret is on the far left or far right##3
2. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
3. the person traveling to marseilles is somewhere to the left of the owner of the bird##5
4. the person traveling to edinburgh and the owner of the turtle have the same parity positions##9
5. the owner of the bird and the person traveling to edinburgh have different parity positions##9
6. the person traveling to marseilles is not to the left of the owner of the pony##8
7. the person traveling to hannover is somewhere to the left of the owner of the pony##5
8. the owner of the ferret is not to the right of the person traveling to hannover##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |     3      |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | ferret | pony | turtle | bird |
| Nationality   | hannover        | marseilles    | edinburgh   | venice |

