.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-9::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: soccer, cricket, weightlifting, handball
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: october, april, june, february
1. the person who's sport is soccer is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in october and the person who's birthday is in april##7
2. the person who's birthday is in april is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in february##8
3. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
4. the person who's sport is handball is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1
5. the person who's sport is cricket is not the person who's birthday is in october##6
6. the person who's sport is weightlifting is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is cricket##5
7. the person who's sport is handball and the person who's birthday is in february have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby   | handball | cricket | soccer | weightlifting |
| Pet     | april     | june     | february     | october    |

