.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-10::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: spy, time-travel, drama, martial-arts
4 different pets are kept: fish, dog, rat, rabbit
1. the owner of the rabbit is not to the left of the person watching spy movies##8
2. the person watching martial-arts movies and the owner of the rabbit have the same parity positions##9
3. the owner of the dog is somewhere to the right of the owner of the rat##5
4. the person watching drama movies is on the left or right of the owner of the dog##3
5. the person watching time-travel movies is somewhere between the owner of the dog and the owner of the rabbit##7
6. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |   3    |     4      |
| Food        | drama | spy   | time-travel | martial-arts |
| Transport   | rat   | dog | fish    | rabbit      |

