.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-17::.
4 different pets are kept: frog, dog, mouse, ferret
4 different games are played: canasta, monopoly, bridge, snooker
 1. the owner of the dog and the person playing bridge have the same parity positions##9
 2. the owner of the mouse is not to the right of the owner of the dog##8
 3. the person playing canasta is somewhere between the owner of the dog and the owner of the frog##7
 4. the person playing bridge is somewhere to the left of the owner of the mouse##5
 5. the owner of the mouse is in an odd position##4
 6. the person playing bridge is not to the left of the owner of the ferret##8
 7. the owner of the ferret and the person playing monopoly have the same parity positions##9
 8. the owner of the ferret is on the left or right of the person playing snooker##3
 9. the person playing snooker is in an odd position##4
10. the owner of the ferret is not to the right of the person playing canasta##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |   3   |    4     |
| Beverage      | frog  | ferret | mouse  | dog |
| Music-Genre   | snooker | bridge     | canasta | monopoly     |

