3. the french is not to the right of the person who growsbellflower##8
4. the nigerian is not to the right of the colombian##8
5. the person who growsbellflower is in an even position##4
6. the person who growsdaisy and the polish have the same parity positions##9
7. the person who growsbellflower and the french have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|       |      1      |   2    |     3      |       4        |
