.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-20::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: aquamarine, grey, mauve, chestnut
City: prague, san-francisco, rome, boston
 1. the person who likes chestnut is on the left of the person traveling to prague##1
 2. the person traveling to rome is on the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
 3. the person traveling to boston is not to the right of the person traveling to rome##8
 4. the person traveling to san-francisco is in an odd position##4
 5. the person traveling to prague is not the person who likes grey##6
 6. the person who likes chestnut is not to the right of the person who likes aquamarine##8
 7. the person who likes chestnut and the person traveling to san-francisco have the same parity positions##9
 8. the person who likes grey is not to the right of the person who likes mauve##8
 9. the person who likes chestnut is the person traveling to san-francisco##1
10. the person who likes grey and the person traveling to san-francisco have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |      2       |    3    |      4      |
| Beverage   | grey    | mauve        | chestnut   | aquamarine      |
| Hobby      | boston | rome | san-francisco | prague |

 